dc_title_s: Agricultural Land Use: Russian River Basin, Sonoma County, California, 19989
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile shows farmland areas within the Sonoma County section of the Russian River Watershed basin in California. The original agricultural land use layer was developed by the Department of Conservation Division Of Land Resource Protection in 1998This layer can be used for land use analysis and planning in the Russian River region of California.
